{"tid":1726304,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"商戶聲明：絕不割蓆","createTime":"2019-11-16T05:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T07:59:33.000Z","uid":304230,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db664a82359c037d1a6856bab56184e7c62e5225","tid":1726304,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opCpNkX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopCpNkX.png&h=29c70c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商戶聲明：<br />\n就算現在營商環境多受影響<br />\n本店絕不埋怨示威者<br />\n更不會與示威者割蓆<br />\n<br />\n你地既心意幫你轉達左比更加有需要既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地自把作為捐哂比星火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12/12先捐比立場 敬請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aaa7e3c4491390fc12811edd65a8e8a3105f315","tid":1726304,"uid":136327,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"成日覺得割蓆呢個字講到前線好似做錯嘢咁，<br />\n絕對<strong>支持</strong>會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw陣間過黎嚴懲你，唔好咁快賣哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752b991e37f6555e232696118e7ec96f13904577","tid":1726304,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:00:13.000Z","msg":"你叫藍絲點跟機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade1112e016537155d61ce9885c6e0ec5d5a688f","tid":1726304,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"多謝藍妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c94fafd2827c5f7a469a0aabb56d5ba5bd25557","tid":1726304,"uid":17381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as